Title: Primal List
Description:
The gateways closed, the elementals slain, and the Primalists stopped... for now.

<Sharnax laughs.>

Is there anything we cannot do, $c? I guess only time will tell.

Take the plans back to the commander. I am certain he will be glad to see we have been successful.
ObjectivesText: Deliver the Bundle of Primalist Orders to Commander Thadezus on the bridge at the Gelikyr Overlook.
ObjectivesCompletionText: Speak with Commander Thadezus at the bridge in Gelikyr Overlook.
RewardText:
<Thadezus pauses for an uncomfortable amount of time.>

Allis and I had bets on if you would be successful, $c

 I am glad that you were.
